{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_03_01",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 03 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――都内、テレビ局",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――At a TV studio in the city.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.2,
      "endTime": 1.4599999904632568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "実は最近、料理にも挑戦中なんです\n体を作るためにも、栄養バランスは自分で考えたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I’ve been trying my hand at cooking lately.\nI want to think about nutritional balance myself‚ for the sake of my body.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666666666666666,
      "endTime": 9.828435484568278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.96
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 10.028435484568277
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-host001.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、料理！\n瑠依ちゃんの手料理を食べられる人は幸せですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ cooking!\nThe person who gets to eat Rui-chan's cooking must be very happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.028435484568277,
      "endTime": 17.399025026957194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 17.595102151234943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "いや～あれが幸せかどうかは\n人によるんちゃうかなぁ？　うちは幸せやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well~ I think whether that’s considered happiness or not\ndepends on the person. I’m happy though~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.595102151234943,
      "endTime": 25.078231461842854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "実は瑠依ちゃん\nすっごく味音痴なんです。だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ Rui-chan\nhas terrible taste. So…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.277866392831015,
      "endTime": 29.717639761666465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 29.911199726164348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと！　そんなことないでしょ？\n美味しく作れているんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey! That’s not true.\nI’m making delicious food.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.911199726164348,
      "endTime": 34.088818754255776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.28881875425577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "アレを美味しい思えることが味音痴の証拠やって\nなんでサラダの色付けにグミをトッピングするんよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking that is delicious is proof of your bad taste.\nWhy would ya top a salad with gummies to add color…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.28881875425577,
      "endTime": 42.502832140028474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.68881875425576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-host002.m4a",
      "text": "トッピングに……グミ？\nな、なるほど。よほどグミが好きなんですね……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gummies as… toppings?\nI see. You must really like gummies…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.68881875425576,
      "endTime": 53.08881913572549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 53.28881913572552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私達で特訓してあげているんです！\n昨日は一緒に、サバの味噌煮を作ったりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ we’re giving her special training!\nWe made miso-simmered mackerel together yesterday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.28881913572552,
      "endTime": 59.96042930036785,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 60.15548580239218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すみれの味付けだって濃かったわよ？\n昨日のだって、やけに味噌が強かったと思うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Sumire‚ your seasoning was too strong too.\nI thought the miso flavor was a bit too overwhelming yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.15548580239218,
      "endTime": 66.65548561165731,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11066.666475931783,
          "startTime": 71.22215227832396
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 66.85548561165731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、サバの味噌煮で味噌薄かったら\nそれただの水煮ちゃうん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if the miso flavor is weak in miso-simmered mackerel‚\nisn’t it just boiled mackerel?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.85548561165731,
      "endTime": 72.1554856116573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 73.08881894499063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、瑠依ちゃんの料理の腕前は\n回を増すごとにちゃ～んと上達してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Rui-chan’s cooking skills\nare definitely improving with each attempt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.08881894499063,
      "endTime": 78.74573489576578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 78.9457348957658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんま、飲み込みが早くてビックリです\nいずれ、うちらも抜かれてしまうかもですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really surprised by how quickly she learns.\nWe might be surpassed someday~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9457348957658,
      "endTime": 85.89573499113322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 86.11240156243247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-host.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-host003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。確かに瑠依ちゃんは多才ですからね\nそういう優ちゃんはどうなんですか？　お料理は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You certainly are multi-talented‚ Rui-chan.\nWhat about you‚ Yu-chan? Do you cook?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.11240156243247,
      "endTime": 93.50283229897421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 93.71240156243245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちは……まあ、ぼちぼちって所ですねぇ\nトリエルのお料理番長はすみれちゃんなんで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me… Well‚ I’m okay at it~\nSumire-chan is the head chef of TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.71240156243245,
      "endTime": 102.23741243431964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 102.44573489576574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！？　私、いつからお料理番長になったの？\nでも、三人でご飯を食べる時は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?! When did I become the head chef?\nBut when the three of us eat together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.44573489576574,
      "endTime": 108.9866644993424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 109.81240156243237
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 109.87906822909898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……爪痕残せた収録やったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… That was a recording where we really left our mark~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.41240156243234,
      "endTime": 115.71240156243233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 115.91240156243234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "観覧席の人達もスタッフさんも\nみ～んな反応良かったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The audience‚ the staff…\nEveryone’s reaction was great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.91240156243234,
      "endTime": 121.97231071541695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。味音痴のくだり以外は、いい感じだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true. It went well‚ except for the part about my bad taste.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.17906822909907,
      "endTime": 126.7058710550268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 126.90587105502681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、根に持ち過ぎだよ\nバラエティなんだからこういう一面も見せていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re dwelling on it too much‚ Rui-chan.\nIt’s a variety show‚ you have to show this side of yourself too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.90587105502681,
      "endTime": 133.70117707004147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 133.90587107947994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、うちはし～っかりフォロー入れといたし\n瑠依ちゃんの好感度、うなぎ登りやって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I made sure to cover for ya properly‚\nso Rui-chan’s popularity is skyrocketing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.90587107947994,
      "endTime": 141.56838795951538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 141.77253774614667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "違う、そうじゃなくて\nグミのトッピングは立派な調理だってこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that’s not what I meant.\nI was trying to say that topping with gummies is a legitimate cooking method.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.77253774614667,
      "endTime": 146.95627912493086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
